         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0351.translation" corresp="#zoor0351.transcription">
            <p>Monument of Paulus, <lb/>(son) of Abdalmithabos <lb/>from Petra, <lb/>(who died at
               the age) <lb/>of 8 years</p>
